('c8eb2cc0-cd2f-59ac-aefd-02631aa2e5ee', 'a2d89bc0-aa6e-42b6-bf38-ebfa28cb35d1', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', 'Is ___ any milk in the fridge?', '冰箱裡有牛奶嗎？', 'there', 'this', 'that', 'it', 'Is there...? 用於詢問「某處是否有...」。', 'Is there...? → 有...嗎？', '2026-07-06 10:42:39', '2026-07-06 10:42:39');
